{"tid":586112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"PTT [問卦] 香港人在跩什麼?","createTime":"2018-03-09T08:54:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T06:03:37.000Z","uid":171257,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"21b158ab6703f3e48433819cf7c04c2ec65bf9f3","tid":586112,"uid":171257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T08:54:15.000Z","msg":"之前去香港出差<br />\n待了四天 只覺得服務態度不知道在糟糕什麼<br />\n（服務態度最好的是酒店櫃檯跟機場給錯我機票的國泰航空地勤）<br />\n地又小 東西也貴（冰的飲料還要額外兩塊港幣）<br />\n一堆人邊走邊抽菸<br />\n<br />\n對說國語的人態度也差<br />\n（我會說廣東話 但說沒很流利 服務態度一樣糟糕）<br />\n<br />\n最近又要去了<br />\n想到就頭痛<br />\n<br />\n香港人在跩什麼<br />\n有沒有八卦?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1520583427.A.7E8.html?from=mopttptt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FGossiping%2FM.1520583427.A.7E8.html%3Ffrom%3Dmopttptt&d=bDcA%2BvpgglXda%2FJiIXtek%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=e36453ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/Gossiping/M.1520583427.A.7E8.html?from=mopttptt</a>"},{"pid":"ed3d245bb35ea4c49dea2149cc0d2d44a10bac1e","tid":586112,"uid":121249,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T08:59:09.000Z","msg":"駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02bb073dcde0f3db601308699c0a399cf09c22ef","tid":586112,"uid":85564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T09:04:41.000Z","msg":"搵食姐"},{"pid":"9934f94bac689b7234a38b2b9e2a5a2c8e379ed1","tid":586112,"uid":44277,"like":49,"dislike":1,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T09:06:04.000Z","msg":"9成9以為佢係大陸喱<br />\n貴就因為台灣物價低啫"},{"pid":"e4f4229b8c9c0e783408d4c73d4368570f289ec9","tid":586112,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T09:07:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b8a131f830bf2f7b0aaff72207ff89cf484d938f","tid":586112,"uid":79709,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T09:09:40.000Z","msg":"戇鳩 香港係咁架啦 以為自己去邊撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/n